data.description: Stunning home that features a large in-ground pool with new liner! Great split floor plan with three bedrooms and one and a half bathrooms separate from the large primary bedroom with walk-in closet and en suite that includes a soaking tub, separate shower, and double vanity. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, a gas cooktop, stained cabinets, and stainless steel appliances. Formal dining room and spacious breakfast nook. The living area is large with a remotely controlled fireplace. The garage has plenty of space with ample storage. Big fenced yard and a workshop with electricity. Roof was replaced in 2021. Wired security system and French door refrigerator to remain.
